1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes the IT Asset Catalog,
 asset lifecycle status classifications,
 work order triage and severity classification framework,
 and service level commitments for the Elko County Information Operations Department.
\end_layout

