 Where an existing contract does not include defined service level terms,
 the Assistant IT Director shall identify the gap,
 document it in the IT Asset Catalog,
 and present it to the IT Director no later than ninety (90) days prior to the next available renewal opportunity so that incorporation of vendor SLA terms may be pursued at renewal.
